dc_description_s: This data layer represents hydrography for Brown County, Wisconsin in 2014 [Hydrography Polygons (lakes, ponds, rivers). These were imported from Land Conservation (Tammy Castonia) from her October 18, 2007 shapefile.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For additional information, please see original license/data sharing agreement. For online dataset download, please visit http://www.co.brown.wi.us/departments/?department=85713eda4cdc
